text: Szczepan Kupczak (born 29 November 1992) is a Polish Nordic combined skier who competes internationally.FIS profile He represented Poland at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Poland Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:People from Żywiec County Category:Universiade bronze medalists for Poland Category:Universiade medalists in nordic combined Category:Competitors at the 2013 Winter Universiade
